operation.name: STG_CUSTOMERS
operation.sql:
SELECT
  C_CUSTKEY AS C_CUSTKEY,

operation.name: STG_ORDERS
operation.sql:
SELECT
  O_ORDERKEY AS O_ORDERKEY,
  O_CUSTKEY AS O_CUSTKEY,
  O_ORDERSTATUS AS O_ORDERSTATUS,
  O_TOTALPRICE AS O_TOTALPRICE,
  SPLIT(O_ORDERDATE,'-')[0] as O_ORDERYEAR,
  SPLIT(O_ORDERDATE,'-')[1] as O_ORDERMONTH,
  SPLIT(O_ORDERDATE,'-')[2] as O_ORDERDAY,
  SPLIT(O_ORDERPRIORITY,'-')[1] as PRIORITY,

FROM
  ${ORDERS}

operation.name: AVG_ACCT_BALANCE_BY_MARKET

FROM
  ${STG_CUSTOMERS}
GROUP BY
  C_MKTSEGMENT

operation.name: AVG_ACCT_BALANCE_BY_NATION
operation.sql:

  N_NAME AS N_NAME,

FROM
  ${STG_DIM_CUSTOMERS_WITH_NATION}
  GROUP BY N_NAME

operation.name: ORDERS_BY_MONTH
operation.sql:
SELECT

  O_ORDERYEAR AS O_ORDERYEAR,
  O_ORDERMONTH AS O_ORDERMONTH
FROM
  ${STG_ORDERS}
  GROUP BY O_ORDERYEAR, O_ORDERMONTH

  GROUP BY CC_MANAGER

operation.name: PHYSICAL_FOOTPRINTS
operation.sql:
SELECT
  COUNT (DISTINCT STG_CALL_CENTER.CC_CALL_CENTER_SK) AS NUM_CALL_CENTERS,
  COUNT (DISTINCT STG_STORE.S_STORE_SK) AS NUM_STORES,
  COUNT (DISTINCT STG_WAREHOUSE.W_WAREHOUSE_SK) AS NUM_WAREHOUSES,
  CC_STATE
FROM
  ${STG_CALL_CENTER} AS STG_CALL_CENTER
  INNER JOIN ${STG_STORE} AS STG_STORE ON STG_CALL_CENTER.CC_STATE = STG_STORE.S_STATE
  INNER JOIN ${STG_WAREHOUSE} AS STG_WAREHOUSE ON STG_STORE.S_STATE = W_STATE
GROUP BY
  CC_STATE

operation.name: HIGHEST_COST_PARTS
operation.sql:
SELECT
  ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
    order by
      PS_SUPPLYCOST desc
  ) AS SupplyCostRank,
  PS_SUPPLYCOST as SupplyCost,
  SUPPLIERID,
  S_PHONE,
  S_NAME
FROM
  ${PARTS_WITH_SUPPLIER}

  S_NAME AS S_NAME,

  S_ACCTBAL AS S_ACCTBAL,
  S_COMMENT AS S_COMMENT,
  PS_PARTKEY AS PS_PARTKEY,
  PS_AVAILQTY AS Part_Quantity,
  ROW_NUMBER() over (order by PS_AVAILQTY asc ) AS PART_QUANTITY_RANK_RANK
FROM
  ${PARTS_WITH_SUPPLIER}

operation.name: CHEAPEST_SUPPLIER_FOR_PART
operation.sql:
WITH RANKED_SUPPLIERS_BY_PART_COST AS (
  SELECT
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
      PARTITION BY PS_PARTKEY
      order by
        PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC
    ) AS SupplyCostRank,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUPPLIERID,
    S_PHONE,
    S_NAME,
    PS_PARTKEY,
    PS_COMMENT
  FROM
    ${PARTS_WITH_SUPPLIER}
)
SELECT
  PS_PARTKEY,
  PS_COMMENT,
  PS_SUPPLYCOST,
  SUPPLIERID,
  S_PHONE,
  S_NAME
FROM
  RANKED_SUPPLIERS_BY_PART_COST
WHERE
  SupplyCostRank = 1

operation.name: CHEAPEST_SUPPLIER_FOR_PART
operation.sql:
WITH RANKED_SUPPLIERS_BY_PART_COST AS (
  SELECT
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
      PARTITION BY PS_PARTKEY
      order by
        PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC
    ) AS SupplyCostRank,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUPPLIERID,
    S_PHONE,
    S_NAME,
    PS_PARTKEY,
    PS_COMMENT
  FROM
    ${PARTS_WITH_SUPPLIER}
)
SELECT
  PS_PARTKEY,
  PS_COMMENT,
  PS_SUPPLYCOST,
  SUPPLIERID,
  S_PHONE,
  S_NAME
FROM
  RANKED_SUPPLIERS_BY_PART_COST
WHERE
  SupplyCostRank = 1

operation.name: CHEAPEST_SUPPLIER_FOR_PART
operation.sql:
WITH RANKED_SUPPLIERS_BY_PART_COST AS (
  SELECT
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
      PARTITION BY PS_PARTKEY
      order by
        PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC
    ) AS SupplyCostRank,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUPPLIERID,
    S_PHONE,
    S_NAME,
    PS_PARTKEY,
    PS_COMMENT
  FROM
    ${PARTS_WITH_SUPPLIER}
)
SELECT
  PS_PARTKEY,
  PS_COMMENT,
  PS_SUPPLYCOST,
  SUPPLIERID,
  S_PHONE,
  S_NAME
FROM
  RANKED_SUPPLIERS_BY_PART_COST
WHERE
  SupplyCostRank = 1

  SELECT
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
      PARTITION BY PS_PARTKEY
      order by
        PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC
    ) AS SupplyCostRank,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUPPLIERID,
    S_PHONE,
    S_NAME,
    PS_PARTKEY,
    PS_COMMENT
  FROM
    ${PARTS_WITH_SUPPLIER}
)
SELECT
  PS_PARTKEY,
  PS_COMMENT,
  PS_SUPPLYCOST,
  SUPPLIERID,
  S_PHONE,
  S_NAME
FROM
  RANKED_SUPPLIERS_BY_PART_COST
WHERE
  SupplyCostRank = 1

operation.name: CHEAPEST_SUPPLIER_FOR_PART
operation.sql:
WITH RANKED_SUPPLIERS_BY_PART_COST AS (
  SELECT
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
      PARTITION BY PS_PARTKEY
      order by
        PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC
    ) AS SupplyCostRank,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUPPLIERID,
    S_PHONE,
    S_NAME,
    PS_PARTKEY,
    PS_COMMENT
  FROM
    ${PARTS_WITH_SUPPLIER}
)
SELECT
  PS_PARTKEY,
  PS_COMMENT,
  PS_SUPPLYCOST,
  SUPPLIERID,
  S_PHONE,
  S_NAME
FROM
  RANKED_SUPPLIERS_BY_PART_COST
WHERE
  SupplyCostRank = 1
